    <note>Lu(2) Zhan [1278] His ancestors were Fufeng jun Lu(2). Yin's [3628] brother, Keju's [7298] uncle and Kefeng's [7299] father. Husband of Fan(2) Zhixu's [8042] niece. His brother's son-in-law, Sun(1) Xiongfei [3775], who was awarded the jinshi in 1132, was a member of a Suzhou lineage and had sons or nephews who included Shaoxian [3778] (jinshi, 1166), Shaoting [3779] (juren, 1165), Shaozu [3780] (juren, 1171) and Shaoyuan [3781], who was Hubei yunpan in 1187. Jiahe zhi, 15.3a; Zhang Shou, WJ, 12.15a-20a; Jiangsu jin, 11.7a, 7b; Zhou Bida, WJ, 32.7a; Fujian TZ, 32.17a; XNYL, 43.2a, 6a; Ge Shengzhong, WJ, 13.20a-23a; Shengzheng, 64.13a; YLDD, 2368.5b, 6b. CBD, 5, 3821.</note>
